Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.39,0:01:02.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.08,0:01:02.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.67,0:01:04.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜的藏身处被死鬼队知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.76,0:01:52.40,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,三年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.83,0:01:55.88,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,遭到压倒性的古拉多斯的力量蹂躏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.33,0:01:58.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,地球上70%的都市被烧毁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.41,0:02:02.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,失去了三分之一的人口
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.30,0:02:07.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,然后 古拉多斯在这破坏之上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.73,0:02:10.77,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,实行了恐怖统治
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.44,0:02:13.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,如神般的君临整个地球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.53,0:02:18.53,Layzner_Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(720,760)\c&H1E17C0&}被{\c&HFFFFFF&}盯上的安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:21.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,并非是为了逃亡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.45,0:02:26.30,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,之所以不移开目光 即不是为了伤害我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.80,0:02:30.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,也不是默默等着世人的背叛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:31.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:35.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我不责备这世界 也不侮辱这世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.04,0:02:38.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,对于一个人的那许多挑战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.11,0:02:41.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,虽然无法估计
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.28,0:02:44.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法提前避免是很愚蠢的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.29,0:02:48.73,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,就算这失误将导致悔恨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.13,0:02:51.05,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,会超越曾经的痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.75,0:02:52.99,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.93,0:02:55.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无论它夺走什么
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.56,0:02:58.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,都无法夺走你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.79,0:03:03.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,从消失的过去的残骸中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.12,0:03:06.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,至少还能想起这一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.37,0:03:09.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那些追忆教会了我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.91,0:03:12.86,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,无法忘记的人 正是最爱之人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.35,0:03:16.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,沙漠之中也有清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.97,0:03:18.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,广阔荒野中也有树木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.15,0:03:22.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,笼中小鸟在孤独中歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:25.52,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我的心中有你的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.28,0:03:31.28,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,沙漠之中也有清泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.59,0:03:33.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,广阔荒野中也有树木
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.08,0:03:38.73,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没错啊 我们就算在逆境中也不能失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.47,0:03:40.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不要失去希望
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,书籍被焚毁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:48.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,已经所剩无几
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.25,0:03:55.71,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是那所剩无几的书籍 居然能给人们带来如此的勇气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.85,0:03:58.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,救 救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:02.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那不是小的的错
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:06.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你不光放跑了英二 还损失了我给的SPT
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.21,0:04:10.27,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,请饶了小的 只要再给小的一次机会我肯定
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.27,0:04:10.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没门
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:12.73,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你要接受惩罚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:15.87,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,想活下来继续帮我做事 就打倒刽子手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.08,0:04:18.75,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那样的话就当你狗运好 饶你一命
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.29,0:04:39.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,曼杰罗 波恩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.92,0:04:42.91,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,住手啊 我们不是好兄弟来的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.80,0:04:56.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.31,0:05:27.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,基乌拉大尉 求见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.37,0:05:41.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这是安娜·史蒂芬妮的记录文件
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.59,0:05:48.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这个小妞最近好像成了反抗分子的指导者啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.17,0:05:50.42,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,啊 正是如此
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.77,0:05:53.18,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在她已经渐渐成了被那帮人所仰慕的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,到了黑名单的顶部
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:06:00.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再这样放任下去 难道不会成为第二个库斯科的圣女吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:02.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有这种可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.53,0:06:05.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那么为什么到现在都还没有做掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.09,0:06:06.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这 这个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.96,0:06:10.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,因为这小妞有英二保护 很棘手
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.08,0:06:11.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,蠢货
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.53,0:06:16.74,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,正因为有英二在才要让他知道厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:18.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,小 小的该死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.12,0:06:21.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,小妞就交给死鬼队解决
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.88,0:06:23.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你去准备
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.96,0:06:25.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那么 是要叫那帮怪物协助吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.09,0:06:28.99,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不能让那些家伙觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:32.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有英二在就安全了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.16,0:06:35.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,叫死鬼队杀鸡儆猴
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.46,0:06:39.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你只要找到小妞的所在就够了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.47,0:06:40.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.36,0:06:40.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.90,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在那里 组装到那台SPT上
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.45,0:06:52.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,把那边的那个搬过来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.97,0:06:58.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们好像一点都没进步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.48,0:06:58.81,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,欸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.92,0:07:03.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,美国和苏联三年前还在做军备竞赛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:07.32,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这次轮到我们和古拉多斯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.01,0:07:12.27,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是啊 为了战斗制造更强大的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.55,0:07:15.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但这是抵抗运动 不是战争
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.33,0:07:18.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们所对抗的不是古拉多斯人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.21,0:07:20.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,而是他们的权利
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.19,0:07:22.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,呦 还好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:26.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:27.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.33,0:07:30.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你所说的钢材不好搞啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.81,0:07:36.10,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在急缺啊 至少要够这电脑系统和燃料引擎系统用
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.91,0:07:48.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,给我地毯式搜查
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.49,0:07:50.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可疑的家伙全带走
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.19,0:08:15.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么会 大家被
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:16.43,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.70,0:08:19.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我看到许多人被抓走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.51,0:08:22.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,总之 我们快逃比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.39,0:08:25.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是这里很安全啊 一直以来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.16,0:08:28.97,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,现在不同了啊 改造队有怪物在
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.13,0:08:31.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他们在乱来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.55,0:08:36.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,真的会吃不了兜着走啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.71,0:08:38.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这里不能说是安全啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.71,0:08:43.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜 也许马修说得没错 暂时离开这里比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.49,0:08:44.46,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是啊 安娜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.48,0:08:46.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.03,0:08:47.81,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大家抓紧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.19,0:08:56.60,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜 向南罗特镇逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.92,0:08:59.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜 这主意不错 那里应该安全
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.09,0:09:02.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,他们知道你的长相
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.28,0:09:04.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你快走 这里就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.20,0:09:08.82,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,书只要藏好 剩下的就可以放心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.88,0:09:09.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.56,0:09:10.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不用担心
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:12.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我都有准备
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:13.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.32,0:09:33.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,知道那个叫安娜的小妞在哪里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.16,0:09:38.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,知道的老实交代 这样马上就会释放你们
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.44,0:09:42.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不说就送去做苦工 不怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.19,0:09:45.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,哼 算了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.83,0:09:48.17,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,等会一个个审
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.26,0:09:50.04,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,基乌拉大尉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.82,0:09:53.49,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.65,0:09:56.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那老头就由本大人亲自料理
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:03.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么样 你知道安娜·史蒂芬妮在哪里吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.11,0:10:07.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,老实招了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.36,0:10:10.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么样 反正你留着这种东西
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.25,0:10:14.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么也逃不过做苦工了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.00,0:10:18.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你要是招了 我就放你一马
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.51,0:10:21.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.20,0:10:22.95,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.25,0:10:24.48,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,有的是时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.33,0:10:26.82,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们慢慢聊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.25,0:10:32.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,干 干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:36.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我觉得你这么做太麻烦了 想帮帮你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.11,0:10:39.39,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,住 住手 不住手我可开枪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.73,0:10:40.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,别这么吓唬人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.96,0:10:41.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你 你干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:45.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,喂 老头 快说小妞在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:49.06,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.77,0:10:51.99,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,给我开枪打死这俩
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:53.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你来真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.47,0:10:56.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这是我的工作 不会让你们乱来的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.67,0:10:58.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,哼 我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.68,0:11:03.72,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,用这种态度对我们 过后你会后悔的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.79,0:11:04.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,随便你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.84,0:11:05.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再会了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.52,0:11:07.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,哼 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.10,0:11:09.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.89,0:11:11.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伤这么重
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:12.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.64,0:11:13.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,得快问出藏身处
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.12,0:11:15.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,喂 拿那个来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.28,0:11:15.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.56,0:11:40.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜·史蒂芬妮的藏身处查出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.32,0:11:44.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,潜伏在郊外的南罗特镇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.32,0:11:45.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,南罗特镇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:45.76,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:50.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,居民已经被改造队清除 现在无人居住
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.85,0:11:53.21,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可是那两个怪物太伤脑筋了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.56,0:11:56.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,明明只会杀人 居然插手审问的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.49,0:11:59.84,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,差点害我失去情报源
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.60,0:12:07.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那么 阁下 接下来请您随意差遣那两个怪物做掉小妞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.47,0:12:08.57,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,报告结束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.63,0:12:09.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.56,0:12:11.54,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你去通知那两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.60,0:12:14.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,欸 我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.41,0:12:15.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,明白了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.33,0:12:17.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.32,0:12:23.70,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,得快点去啊 那里可是半个人都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.76,0:12:27.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我们再不快去 安娜她们可要吓坏了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.57,0:12:37.15,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,伤脑筋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.33,0:12:40.53,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 帮我拿千斤顶来 我去拿扳手
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.64,0:12:41.43,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.21,0:13:04.02,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,嘿嘿 马上就到了 马上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.88,0:13:09.05,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么 那么安娜来联络了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.23,0:13:11.09,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那个 那里没有无线电
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.32,0:13:14.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,大卫他们呢 说是去了安娜那里了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.59,0:13:16.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,得到情报的时候 他们已经出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.99,0:13:24.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,要赶上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,找到了啊 找到了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.99,0:13:46.61,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:49.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜的藏身处被死鬼队知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.75,0:13:50.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.44,0:13:51.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.11,0:13:52.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜有危险 快去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.04,0:13:54.21,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.32,0:13:55.27,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.35,0:14:26.51,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么了 多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.39,0:14:29.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.20,0:14:58.68,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没什么奇怪的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.07,0:15:00.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,怎么了啊 多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.59,0:15:05.97,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜 上面
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.52,0:15:15.36,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,是二楼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.15,0:15:29.45,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,好像不是这上面啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.77,0:16:21.89,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,波恩 你还要跟狗玩多久
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.01,0:16:23.35,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,小妞逃上去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.76,0:16:38.20,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,安娜 你在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:46.76,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,这混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.63,0:17:04.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.71,0:17:09.80,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:12.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,马修
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.12,0:17:21.83,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:25.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,西蒙尼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.47,0:17:26.07,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.49,0:18:03.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你去上面
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.11,0:18:03.73,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.85,0:18:31.40,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,老 老子的俊脸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.07,0:18:32.92,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:43.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,竟敢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.41,0:18:46.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,老子杀了你 杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.48,0:19:06.19,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.43,0:19:07.11,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你那边呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.35,0:19:08.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,让他逃了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.52,0:19:09.55,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.57,0:19:10.55,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,你们都没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.17,0:19:12.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,跑掉的肯定还会回来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.89,0:19:13.79,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,此地不宜久留
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.87,0:19:18.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.56,0:19:21.33,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.84,0:19:24.63,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.57,0:19:28.52,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,别管我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.99,0:19:29.44,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,快跑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.73,0:19:31.41,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,该死的英二 老子杀了你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.80,0:19:34.37,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,波恩 住手 我来杀那小子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.49,0:19:38.24,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,波恩 放开英二
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.64,0:19:42.67,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,再不放老子连你一起杀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.04,0:19:54.47,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,曼杰罗那混蛋 连我也想杀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.76,0:19:55.88,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,饶不了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.27,0:20:07.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.75,0:20:22.03,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,连雷兹纳一起做掉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.07,0:20:26.65,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,警告信息 过重警告
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.84,0:20:28.64,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,机动力减少0.72
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.64,0:20:29.29,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,甩掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.55,0:20:49.01,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,雷 V-MAX准备
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.11,0:20:50.23,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,V-MAX启动中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.24,0:20:57.66,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,曼杰罗 你也一起下地狱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.28,0:21:07.13,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,波恩这混蛋 这样我也要被干掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.32,0:21:09.96,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,放开了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.16,0:21:11.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,雷 V-MAX发动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.65,0:21:12.08,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,已启动
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.37,0:22:15.26,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,英二
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.24,0:22:38.43,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.88,0:22:45.93,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.16,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.41,0:22:51.25,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,多乌
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.57,0:23:56.69,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,为什么觉得我不会开枪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.00,0:23:58.00,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我会的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.36,0:23:59.56,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,那就开吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.48,0:24:02.59,Default_Sub,,0,0,0,,我爱英二啊
